videos.description: Danny Etling looked good on the opening drive with a 36-yard TD dart to Drake Davis.
videos.headline: Etling bombs one to Davis for the LSU score

videos.description: Derrius Guice shows off his strength and side-step for the score.
videos.headline: Guice powers in for the TD

videos.description: Derrius Guice gets another short-yardage score for LSU.
videos.headline: Guice twice as nice with his second TD

videos.description: LSU's D.J. Chark leaves the punt coverage team in his wake with a speedy TD return.
videos.headline: Chark takes the punt 65 yards to the house

videos.description: Darrel Williams runs it in from four yards out.
videos.headline: Williams joins in on the scoring fun

videos.description: Darrel Williams gets his second TD of the game as the Tigers keep rolling.
videos.headline: LSU pours it on with fourth rushing TD

videos.description: Darrell Bridges snakes his way in for the Mocs' first TD
videos.headline: Chattanooga finally finds the end zone

videos.description: The Tigers excelled in the passing game to go along with four rushing touchdowns in an easy win over Chattanooga.
videos.headline: Highlihgts and Analysis from LSU's dominating win

videos.description: D.J. Clark's 65-yard punt return TD highlights LSU's big day as it defeats Chattanooga 45-10.
videos.headline: LSU routs Chattanooga 45-10
